---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Business Leaders India — original news synthesis from regional and international press."
>
  <article class="article-prose max-w-prose">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Business Leaders India</h1>

    <p>
      Business Leaders India is an original-news site for an Indian audience. Each piece is
      synthesised from multiple regional and international press reports and rewritten in plain
      English with the human angle foregrounded.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial principles</h2>
    <p>
      Conversational, credible, human. We translate corporate moves into what they mean for
      everyday people. We attribute claims. We never invent humans, quotes, or scenarios that do
      not appear in our source material.
    </p>

    <h2>Our beats</h2>
    <p>Business, Finance, Entertainment, Sports, Lifestyle, Health, Travel, International News, and Vedic Astrology.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Tips, corrections, and feedback: see our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
